title: [The Restless years : publicity kit]
brief_description: Publicity kit for the production The Restless Years (TV 1977-1982), including 8 B&W Stills (Large). Includes stills of Nick Hedstrom, Julieanne Newbould, Victoria Nicolls, Tom Burlinson, Jon Blake, Simon Burke, Peter Phelps
